* COPY INTO
** How it Works
***_ Batch SQL command
***_ Idempotent - skips processed files
***_ Tracking via Delta transaction log
** Best For
***_ One-time data migrations
***_ Scheduled batch loads
***_ SQL-first workflows
** Advantages
***_ Simple configuration
***_ No streaming infrastructure
***_ Predictable behavior
** vs. Auto Loader
***_ COPY INTO: one-time batch
***_ Auto Loader: ongoing incremental
@endmindmap
